<xref type="reprint from" targOrder="U" from="ROOT" to="DITTO" n="chr.mitt;;72" evaluate="all">MChr72</xref></head><div type="edition" lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">
    <lb n="1"/>Φ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">λα</supplied>ουίῳ <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">Ἰσὰ</unclear>κ<g type="apostrophe"/> τῷ λογιωτάτῳ σχολαστικῷ ἐκδίκῳ τῆς ἄνω Κυνοπολιτῶν 

    <lb n="2"/><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">παρὰ</supplied> Αὐρηλίου Μακαρίου υἱοῦ <hi rend="diaeresis">Ἰ</hi>ωσὴφ ἀπὸ τῆς αὐτῆς πόλεως. 

    <lb n="3"/>πρ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ὸ τ</supplied>ούτου <hi rend="diaeresis">ὑ</hi>δροπάροχος καθέστηκα καὶ γεωργὸς φανερῶν πραγμάτων οὐσίας 

    <lb n="4"/>τοῦ <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">τῆ</supplied>ς μακαρίας μνήμης Φοιβ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ά</supplied>μμωνος τοῦ πολιτευ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">σα</unclear>μένου, μετὰ δὲ τὴν τούτου τελευτὴν 

    <lb n="5"/>ὁ τ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ούτ</supplied>ου ἀδελφὸς Θεόδωρος <choice><corr>ἐπεισῆλθεν</corr><sic>επισηλθεν</sic></choice> εἰς τὴν φροντίδα τῶν τούτου πραγμάτων 

    <lb n="6"/>κ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">αὶ τυρ</supplied>αννικῷ τρόπῳ ἀπέσπασεν ὀκτὼ <num value="8"/> καλὰ <subst><add place="inline">ἐκ</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable"><gap reason="illegible" extent="1" unit="character"/>κ</del></subst> τῶν ἐμῶν βο<hi rend="diaeresis">ι</hi>κῶν ζῴων 

    <lb n="7"/><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">καὶ</unclear> <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ἐστεί</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">λ</unclear>ατο καὶ παρεσκεύασέν με ἀδίκως ἀναλημφθῆναι τῷ δεσμωτηρίῳ πρὸ 

    <lb n="8"/>τριῶν <num value="3"/> τούτων μηνῶν, καὶ ἐκ τούτου συνέβη τὸ ὑπόλοιπον τῶν ἐμῶν ζῴων 

    <lb n="9"/>τῇ λιμῷ τεθνάναι, ταῦτα ἐμοῦ ἑτοίμως ἔχοντος εἰ καὶ φανείην <choice><corr>χρεωστῶν</corr><sic>χρεωστουντα</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="10"/>αὐτῷ ἐγγράφως πληρῶσαι. <choice><corr>ἐπεὶ</corr><sic>επι</sic></choice> τοίνυν οἱ ἔκδικοι ἐπενοήθησαν ἐν ταῖς <choice><corr>πόλεσιν</corr><sic>πολεσειν</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="11"/>πρὸ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ς</supplied> <choice><corr>τὸ</corr><sic>τω</sic></choice> βοήθειαν ὀρέξαι <subst><add place="inline">τ<add place="supralinear">οῖ</add>ς</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">τ<del rend="erasure" status="unremarkable">η</del>ς</del></subst> <subst><add place="inline">ἀδικουμέν<add place="supralinear">οι</add>ς</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">αδικουμεν<del rend="erasure" status="unremarkable">η</del>ς</del></subst>, εἰς τελείαν γὰρ ἀνατροπὴν καὶ εἰς <choice><corr>ἐσχάτην</corr><sic>αιχατην</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="12"/><choice><corr>πεῖναν</corr><sic>πεινων</sic></choice> περιέστην ἕνεκεν τοῦ προειρημένου πολιτευομένου, τούσδε τοὺς λιβέλλους 

    <lb n="13"/>ἐπιδίδωμι τῇ σῇ <choice><corr>λογιότητι</corr><sic>λογιοτιτι</sic></choice> ἀξιῶν κελεῦσαι τοῦτον μετασταλῆναι <app type="BL"><lem resp="1.328"><choice><corr>πρωτοτύπως</corr><sic>πρωτοδηπως</sic></choice></lem><rdg><choice><corr>πρῶτο<supplied reason="omitted" cert="high">ν</supplied></corr><sic>πρωτο</sic></choice> δή πωσ</rdg></app> μὲν 

    <lb n="14"/>παρασκε<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">υάσαι</supplied> τὴν αὐτοῦ ἀρετὴν ἀποδοῦναί μοι ἅπερ ἀπέσπασεν τυραννικῷ τρόπῳ βοικά μου 

    <lb n="15"/>ζῷα εὐθαλῆ καθὼς καὶ <subst><add place="inline">ἀπέσπασεν</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">απεσ<gap reason="illegible" extent="1" unit="character"/>ασεν</del></subst>, περὶ δὲ τῶν ἄλλων τὰ δοκοῦντα τῇ σῇ λογιότητι πρα-

    <lb n="16"/>χθῆναι <choice><corr>ἀνεθ<supplied reason="omitted" cert="high">ῆ</supplied>ναί</corr><sic>ανεθναι</sic></choice> <app type="BL"><lem resp="1.328">τ᾽ ἐμὲ</lem><rdg>τέ με</rdg></app> τῶν δεσμῶν <add place="supralinear"><del rend="erasure" status="unremarkable"><gap reason="illegible" extent="unknown" unit="character" desc="vestiges"/></del></add>, ἐμοῦ ὡς προεῖπον ἑτοίμως ἔχοντος πληρῶσαι 

    <lb n="17"/>ὅσα <choice><corr>ἐποφείλω</corr><sic>εποφιλω</sic></choice> αὐτῷ ἐγγράφως· <subst><add place="inline"><choice><corr>μισοῦσιν</corr><sic>μισουσειν</sic></choice></add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">μιζουσειν</del></subst> γὰρ οἱ νόμοι τοὺς τὰ ἄδικα διαπρατ<g type="apostrophe"/>το-

    <lb n="18"/>μέν<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ο</supplied>υς, λογιώτατε ἔκδικε κύριε. <handShift new="m2"/> Αὐρήλιος Μακάριος Ἰωσὴφ ἐπιδέδωκα. 

    <lb n="19"/><handShift new="m3"/> μετὰ <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">τ</supplied>ὴν ὑπατείαν Φλ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">α</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ουίο</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">υ</unclear> Βιβιανοῦ τοῦ λαμπροτάτου τὸ <num value="2">β</num> καὶ τοῦ δηλωθησομένου Ἁθὺρ <num value="24">κδ</num>. </ab></div><div n="meta.20368" type="description" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><rs type="material" cert="high">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.20368" type="commentary" subtype="textDate" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><date type="textDate" value="0464-11-20" notBefore="464" notAfter="464">20. Nov. 464</date></p></div><div n="meta.20368" type="commentary" subtype="general" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p>Zur Datierung vgl. CSBE, S. 119 und P.Oxy. LXXII 4914,1-2 Anm.</p></div><div n="meta.20368" type="commentary" subtype="mentionedDates" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>Erwähnte Daten</head></div><div n="meta.20368" type="bibliography" subtype="principalEdition" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="publication" subtype="principal" default="NO"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Oxy.</title><biblScope type="volume">6</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">902</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos" default="NO"><biblScope type="numbers">20368</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP" default="NO"><series>0181</series>; <biblScope type="volume">6</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">902</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref type="Perseus" href="0181;6;902" evaluate="all" from="ROOT" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.20368" type="bibliography" subtype="illustrations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.20368" type="bibliography" subtype="otherPublications" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>Andere Publikation</head><bibl 